http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/chennai/Vishal-refutes-charge-of-graft-in-Nadigar-Sangam/article14596138.ece

Refuting allegations that the Nadigar Sangam has indulged in corruption, the association secretary, actor Vishal, said that the accounts were at the sangam office for anyone to see and the allegations were baseless.A section of junior artistes (members of the Sangam) had made the allegations that there was corruption to the tune of Rs. 3 crore and that many promises made during the polls had not been fulfilled.“We have been functioning in a transparent manner and there is no truth in the allegations that we are corrupt,” Mr. Vishal told reporters.